# Change Log
## [v1.4.0](https://www.kronops.com.mx) (2021-07-23)
**Features**

* Adds playbooks to get some aplications on your system, including:
  * Brave browser
  * Telegram messenger
  * Kitty terminal
  * Github CLI

## [v1.3.0](https://www.kronops.com.mx) (2021-04-11)

**Features*

* Update playbooks for kubuntu 20.04 (focal).
* Add ansible playbooks for anydesk.

**Fixes*

* Update playbook metadata for kubuntu 20.04 (focal).
* Update readme with more instructions, best practices and how to contribute.

## [v1.2.0](https://www.kronops.com.mx) (2020-12-30)

**Features*

* Add ansible playbooks for apt & source repositories.
* Add ansible playbooks for shell settings.
* Add ansible playbooks for KDE packages for audio & video.
* Add ansible plabybooks for common desktop users with cli and X11 tools.
* Add ansible playboooks for web browsing with firefox & chrome, emailing with thunderbird.
* Add ansible playbook for productivity tools like freeplane.
* Add ansible playbooks for teamviewer, insync, zoom and slack.
* Add ansible playbooks for developer tools like atok, virtualbox, vagrant, packer, gcloud,
  aws cli, terraform & docker.

